Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the city of Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:31.01,Main Dialogue,Hinoko,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:05.98,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,My Talent Is Being a Scarecrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:15.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure the place I'm staying \Nwas right around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:18.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't see a building \Nthat looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.32,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.02,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That girl has chicks on her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.71,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:32.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo has so many buildings and \Ntrain tracks, it's like a maze...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:35.21,Main Dialogue,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.28,Main Dialogue,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.70,Main Dialogue,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of \Ndead-end streets in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:41.70,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.93,Main Dialogue,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big bag. Did you just move to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.93,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.68,Main Dialogue Top,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a student? Is the place \Nyou're heading to near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:48.07,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Which question should I answer first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.98,Main Dialogue Top,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, that restaurant \Nhas great Russian cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.86,Main Dialogue Top,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, when \Nmy daughter came here yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.86,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe I should introduce myself first...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.36,Main Dialogue Top,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,she got lost and had a pretty rough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:57.34,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better not say anything that \Nwould offend someone from Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.01,Main Dialogue,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,A scarecrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:29.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I wasn't able to speak well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been bad at talking, \Nso I've practiced a lot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.90,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, tanukis, bunnies, birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.01,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Which story should I read today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.46,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Cinderella?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:48.53,Flashback Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Animals sure do love you, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:51.91,Flashback Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,That keeps the birds out of my fields, \Nso I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.17,Flashback Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even need a scarecrow anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.42,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.16,Flashback Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! You froze up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.13,Flashback Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:06.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I was always \Nbeing put to work as a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:11.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got into the \Nhigh school of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to at least try to \Nnot freeze up in front of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:17.15,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,-Japanese\NThere's a quiz tomorrow\N{\c&H0000DD&}We covered most of it yesterday\N{\c&H7C6055&}-PE is basketball, \Nso prepare gym shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:17.15,Note - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,-We're going to be doing oil painting in art, \Nso wear clothes and an apron that can get dirty\N{\c&H0000DD&}Preparations are necessary, \Nso get to the art room early
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and be able to talk easily with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And while I was worrying about that, \NI made it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.99,Used Bookstore Hitotose,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore \N{\fs28}Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I'm staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:33.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure\N it's the right address, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That employee is so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Is she reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Or... eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.64,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:10.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that I could stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.70,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're Hinako-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.21,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady's told me all about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The second floor is used for apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.99,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where I live, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.71,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Kuina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get the landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.72,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA2FE3&}-Thank you for letting me borrow the textbook yesterday!\N-The book I borrowed is inside the desk.\N{\c&H000000&}-Sorry I couldn't return it to you in person.\N{\c&HBA2FE3&}-You're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.72,Note - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&}-If you ever need anything let me know.\N-Thank you so much!\NLets hang out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Some of these books look so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This shop has such a nice atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.98,sign_8176_60_In_the_Forest__U,Text,0000,0000,0000,,In the Forest, Under Cherries in Full Bloom \NSakaguchi Ango
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:56.25,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it looks like \Nthe landlady's out right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you look me in the eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen someone \Neating a book before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.76,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That was... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I love reading,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.76,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,and books are basically my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I adore them so much, I want to eat them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.77,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't eat your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, I'll show you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.68,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This room is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm in a hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A chest with its own atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,a cute bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and even a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.17,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.17,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is there a maid in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.18,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Mayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I live and work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.73,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She's a resident here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.33,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,All residents work here. That's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:06.53,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Schoolwork comes first, though, \Nso it's only on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why Mayu-chan is a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an employee in the coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.94,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is just what I always wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They're your own clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:24.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I heard that someone new \Nwas moving in today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.50,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,so I was just cleaning up this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.63,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan wants to be a princess. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.56,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You like frills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.57,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just rehearsing for when I'm \Ninvited to dances in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.35,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,so I won't step on the hem of my dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.68,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:46.90,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you're starting at \NFujimiya High in spring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I'll have a kouhai there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A kouhai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I was a first-year like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but I'm a second-year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:01.91,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,People always think I look younger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.91,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell her I thought \Nshe was in elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.88,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, it doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.54,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm a first-year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.67,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,The toilet is in the middle of the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.72,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We only have a given amount of time \Nto use the bath, so be careful of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, that's immodest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:25.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.98,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't finish my breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.36,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's noon, anyway. Why don't we have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,In a bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:44.00,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,See? This is the coffee shop where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:48.50,sign_12564_124_Coffee_shop_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee shop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:48.50,sign_12564_125_Used_Bookstore_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:48.50,sign_12564_126_You_Are_Here_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,You Are {\c&H5C5CC0&}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a coffee shop \Nin the back of the bookstore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.26,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.51,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to eat a book, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.14,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is a menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:10.29,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you enroll at our \Nhigh school, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:10.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.35,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:16.66,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I start explaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:21.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Well... when I was a scarecrow \Nout in the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.95,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A scarecrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.47,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You mean those dolls that stand in fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:30.79,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She froze up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,She really does look like a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:39.43,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's practice menu\N-Stretches {\c&HBE6A7F&}<-- Do them properly!\N{\c&H7C6055&}-3 kilo marathon {\c&HBE6A7F&}<-- Try your best not to walk\N{\c&H7C6055&}-Vocal exercises\N-Review the script
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:39.43,Note - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,-Review strong and weak points \Nand check on props\N-Check on costume\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what exactly she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:39.43,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So she literally freezes up \Nand does nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I get nervous easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.89,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual to see someone become \Na scarecrow because of nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:50.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But during my school's field trip last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a theater club play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:56.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was so moved by the \Nactors' bold performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided I wanted to be in theater, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:15.20,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you enrolled \Nat our high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:18.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you two in theater or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're both really cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:23.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and I bet Kuu-chan could write good stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayu-chan could play \Na princess, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:31.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'd probably eat the script \Nright after writing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:37.86,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I could never wear a dress! \NI'd be too embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.15,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But that outfit doesn't embarrass her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:44.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to join \Nthe theater club, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Our school is pretty prestigious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:51.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to talk a lot \Nin front of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.06,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:54.63,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and I want to make lots of friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.76,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:03.26,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the theater club was \Nshut down last year, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:05.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:20.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's my fault for not checking \Nbefore I enrolled there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But, but... there was no Internet \Nout in the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And I just bought that cell phone yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.42,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to join the theater club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:43.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in any other clubs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:46.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm not good at any sports or arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Good at... The only thing I'm good at is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,...being a scarecrow, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:12:00.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Scarecrows wouldn't be \Nof any use in Tokyo, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:08.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to live here, I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:09.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way! I could never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.84,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.51,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:24.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.51,sign_17919_194_Tears,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.35,sign_17947_195_Family_Photo,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}Family Photo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.35,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,...homesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.02,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:36.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. You just moved to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.50,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go out for a change of pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big park nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:47.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really? A park?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:51.12,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of greenery there, \Ntoo. I'm sure you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.28,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place near there \Nthat has great chicken skewers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:56.64,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,and a stand that has great dumplings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.54,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And also ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:02.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No description of the actual park, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:06.13,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, are you hungry again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.89,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're on this road, \Nit's straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.27,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the café there has amazing cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.78,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on. We just ate lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.78,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And once we turn this corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.28,sign_19296_216_Taiyaki,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyaki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kuu-chan, not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:31.78,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're so easily tempted by food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:35.79,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I smelled delicious taiyaki, \Nso I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:40.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're like an older sister, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.42,Italics Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,An older sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:52.07,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Honestly, Kuu-chan, \Nyou're hopeless without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.19,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Your big sister will go buy taiyaki for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.02,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,When did she become our big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.84,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, I'd like three taiyaki, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.53,Main Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.76,Main Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And since you're such a cutie, \NI'll give you a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.75,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.06,Main Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:24.21,sign_20581_234_Taiyaki,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyaki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.28,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.90,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me a discount!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She was our big sister a minute ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:32.55,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and now she's an elementary schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:38.50,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.48,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's crispy on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:47.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,with lots of soft red bean paste \Non the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:50.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think this is the first time \NI've bought food and eaten it on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.74,Flashback Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, are you heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:55.99,Flashback Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Want some watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.03,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hup... hup...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:03.00,Flashback Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a fresh-picked tomato and cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.32,Flashback Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw in a daikon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.00,Flashback Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.68,Italics Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I got most of my food for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.01,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these great?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.00,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,See? Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And the cherry trees are in bloom—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.54,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA2FE3&}I met a kitty cat in town today\N{\c&H7C6055&}It kept meowing\N{\c&H7A210D&}and kept calling to me, so I followed it, \Nand ended up at a gathering spot for kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.54,Note - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H535A12&}There were a lot of cute kitties, \Nand they all came up to me \Nand were friendly.\N{\c&HBA2FE3&}I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.31,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, have you calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:50.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry I worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:54.77,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not many people come \Nover this way, so you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:00.69,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The dumplings from the stand \Nby the entrance were so good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:04.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, Kuu-chan! \NGet your mind off food already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She can eat more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.45,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go look at the ducks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ducks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There are ducks in the pond!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.83,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.29,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.84,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I won't eat the duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:36.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... Kuu-chan, do you like ducks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:39.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Especially the way \Nthey slide through the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so cool, like a stealth fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.35,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... S-Ste...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Isn't it a nice place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:54.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,All the greenery reminds me \Nof the forests out in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was feeling a bit down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.75,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're not homesick anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Homesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.71,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.75,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who killed my friend with this blade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.41,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Identify yourself at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,There are lot of small theater \Ntroupes around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:16.90,Main Dialogue Top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The killer couldn't have been \Nsomeone here. Can't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:19.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,so the aspiring actors and troupe members \Ncome here to practice often.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:21.00,Main Dialogue Top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! The door to this \Nplace was closed the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.93,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:23.88,Main Dialogue Top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And the windows lock from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:26.31,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they're running \Nstraight toward their dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.31,Main Dialogue Top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody could've gotten in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:30.73,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I really do want to go into theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.82,Italics Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.57,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That girl practicing over there is Aki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.32,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.74,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why you weren't at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.58,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't expect to see you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.10,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you were going out, \Nyou should have said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.25,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Vocal practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:55.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, this is a classmate of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,and the landlady of our building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:08.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chiaki, the landlady of Hitotose Manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.82,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's tall and has a nice figure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.70,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.71,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.51,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be in your care starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like an arranged marriage meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:40.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Aki-chan \Nused to be a child actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,She still loves theater to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:48.13,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be in the theater club \Nat Fujimiya High School, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.99,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's normally quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.69,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,but on the stage, she's a different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Her role as a former biker gang member
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:58.26,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,and young proprietress at a traditional \Ninn who's now an idol singer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.95,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,was especially powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:02.45,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of play was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.48,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:17.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I entered Fujimiya High School because \NI wanted to be in its theater club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:21.35,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But when I heard the club was \Nshut down, I was so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.43,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,More accurately, it's on hiatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hiatus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:30.28,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,The club's advisor is on a theater trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's on break in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.40,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's on hiatus because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are the other members doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.57,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,they're all doing \Nthe things they want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:56.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:20:01.34,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to perform \Ntheater that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.38,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you start a theater troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:05.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Small theater troupes \Ndon't need many members.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.35,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd be the leader, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,More accurately, she'd be the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A theater troupe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:22.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Could I really make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.61,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You have members. You'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:25.99,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You have four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:26.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.87,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:31.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are we being dragged into something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.46,sign_29602_353_Hitotose,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel alive again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:52.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So many things happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I met lots of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,went to lots of places,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and experienced lots of firsts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:05.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was sad when I heard \Nthe theater club had been shut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.07,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.08,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Starting a theater troupe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:13.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Could I really do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:22.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Still, all the people at \NHitotose Manor are so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:26.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everything will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:31.38,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're been in here \Nfor a long time. Are you o—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.87,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, hang in there! \NOh, what do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.31,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Get Aki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.10,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:43.58,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:44.98,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! She looks like a boiled octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.30,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "I'm here"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.86,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:48.84,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:49.73,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:34.68,Next Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,6000)}It Begins Here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:29.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really start a theater troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be a scarecrow forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:36.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to remember how I felt on the day \NI decided that's how I wanted to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:39.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "It Begins Here."
